  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad Kung̅s Kehniſsch/ pſtiprini ſcho Bautſli/ un uſrak- i to weenâ Grahmata/ kaſ ne ohp pahrgrohſita/ pehz to Mee- eru un Perſern Bautlibas/ ko e weens drihkſt pahrkahpt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad rakſtiia taſ Kehniſsch Darjuſ tahnu Grahmatu/ un Bautſli.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Dantjels fajutte ahdu Grahmatu rakſtitueſtam/ ahje wiꞥſch ſawa Nammâ/ bet wiꞥſam btj ſawa augſta J- tabâ atwehrſi Lohgt prett Jeru- aleimi/ un wiꞥſch mettehs zaur Deenu trihſreisi Zettôs/ luḥ- ſe/ teize un pateize tawam Dee- vam/ ta ka wiꞥſch pirnak zee- tija darriht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nahze tee Wiḣri lee- â Pultâ preekſch ta Kehniſka/ un fazzija ug to Kehniſzu: Tu ſunt/ Kung̅s Kehniſsch/ ka to Meederu un Perſern Bautliba ſchi irr/ ka wiſs Bautſlis un Likkums/ ko tas Kehniſsch irr eezehtis ne warr pahrgrohſihts tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee peegabje/ un run- naja preekſch to Kehniſu no ta Kehnina Bautſla/ neggt tn effi iſpesti. veenu Likkumu uſrakſtijs/ ka vitis/ kaſ eefſch trihſdefinitis Deenahm no jebkuxra Deewa/ neb Zilweſka ko lab luhaſ/ bes ka io tewis ak Kehniſch! tam bij nauwu Bedrê eemestam tapt? tas Kehniſſch atbiildeja/ un faz- tja: Tas ter teeti/ pehz to Mee- deru un Perſern Bautlibas/ ko neveenam ouhs pahrkahpt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad atbiildeja tee/ un faz- tja preekſch to Kehniſu: Dani-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad tas Kehniſsch ſcho Wallodu dsirdeja/ tappē wiꞥſch pee tewis noſkummis/ un dar- bojahs no wiſfas Sirđs Dant- jela pehz/ ka wiꞥſch to iſpeſitu/ teekams ta Saule nogahje/ mek- leja wiꞥſch to iſglahbt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet tee Wiḣri nahze lee- la Pultâ preekſch ta Kehniſka/ un fazzija ug to Kehniſzu: Tu ſunt/ Kung̅s Kehniſsch/ ka to Meederu un Perſern Bautliba ſchi irr/ ka wiſs Bautſlis un Likkums/ ko tas Kehniſsch irr eezehtis ne warr pahrgrohſihts tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad pawehleja taſ Keh- niſsch/ ka teem bij Dantjelu at- west/ un wiſsu Lauwu Bedrê eemest/ un tas kehninſch atbil- deja/ un fazzija ug Dantjelu: Taws Drews/ ko tu beſ Mitte- ſchanas gohdi/ tas lui tewi atkat\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Pehz tappē weens Ak- mins atneſts/ un us tahs Bed- res Zauramu likts/ to paſchu aiſ- sehgeleja taſ Kehniſsch ar kawu Gredſenu/ un ar favo Warreno Gredſenn/ ka ta noneſta Teeta pee Danijela ne taptu pahr- grohſita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nogahje taſ Keh- niſsch us tawn Piſſt/ un palik- te zaur Nakti ne-ehtis/ un ne liſte ne kahou Barribu ſew preekſch\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
